<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Thank You | Rangriti</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css"> <!-- your CSS file -->
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
      background-color: #f4e3c1;
      color: #5a3e2b;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .thank-you-container {
      background-color: #fff8ee;
      border: 2px solid #d8c6aa;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(90, 62, 43, 0.2);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 90%;
    }

    .thank-you-container h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #8b5c2f;
    }

    .thank-you-container p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .btn-home {
      background-color: #c9a16b;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 25px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .btn-home:hover {
      background-color: #a87e50;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="thank-you-container">
    <h1>Thank You!</h1>
    <p>Your response has been received. We appreciate your time and support for Rangriti.</p>
    <a href="/index.html" class="btn-home">Return to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>